cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL 

This paper deals with the task of unsupervised bilingual translation, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of statistical models and algorithms for data mining, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of GPU acceleration for computation could also fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DL (Deep Learning).
